e: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Frecuencia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Alta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Existencia de registros en el catálogo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:40.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;El usuario accede al catálogo, el sistema recupera la lista completa de productos [Excepción 1], el sistema despliega una tabla con SKU, Nombre, Categoría, stock actual, estado del stock, unidad de medida y estado “Activo/Inactivo”, el usuario navega por las páginas del listado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:20.25pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: Catálogo vacío. El sistema informa que no hay productos creados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El usuario tiene una visión global del catálogo de la empresa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Dependencias&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(234, 153, 153); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;UR 1.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/b&gt;